title: Looking for Silver/Gold for 5s
body:
Looking for silver to gold players interested in some ranked 5s. Need Adc/Supp/Top lane. 

Usually play from 9pm Brisbane time (11pm NZ) for a good 4-5 hours

Gold 3 flex (generally jungle) and silver 3 mid so far :)

Will be using Skype. Leave a message with rank, lane choice and preferred champions

replies.body: Gold 1- Adc main been looking for a team for a while, will play regularly :)

Gold 5 - medalarm.

I play every role and every champ.

IGN Tempestuous1
Silver IV, main jg, top and adc.
